bilingual.source: The lock had been forced by an intruder.
Is it OK if I lock the door?
Tom, you will lock the door, all right?
Don't forget to lock the door when you go out.
I told my parents I would remember to lock the door when I went out.
bilingual.target: 我告诉父母我出门时会记得锁门。

bilingual.source: Please make sure you have engaged the safety lock.
bilingual.target: 请确保你已经锁上了安全锁。

bilingual.source: The locking plate is broken, so the door can't lock.
bilingual.target: 锁片坏了，所以门不能锁上。

bilingual.source: I forgot to lock the front door.

list.abstract: lock 确保当一个线程位于代码的临界区时，另一个线程不进入临界区。如果其他线程试图进入锁定的代码，则它将一直等待（即被阻止），直到该对象被释放。 线程处理（C# 编程指南） 这节讨论了线程处理。 lock 调用块开始位置的 Enter 和块结束位置的Exit。 通常，应避免锁定 public 类型，否则实例将超出代码的控制范围。

yingyinNormal.en: I have to get a lock for my door.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我一定要给我的门弄个锁。

yingyinNormal.en: Does that room have a closet I can lock him in? We'll take it. Great.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那个房间有个衣橱可以让我把他锁起来吗？我们要那间房。太好了。

yingyinNormal.en: I swear I didn't. Hey. Is that why you guys used to go up to your bedroom and lock the door? Yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道，所以你们才会常把房门锁上吗？对。

yingyinNormal.en: They just wanna ransom us. I heard them. They're gonna lock us in that van, and then drive it into the river.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们只求钱财，我听他们说他们会把我们锁进货车，然后丢到河里。

yingyinNormal.en: No. We'll protect her. She can learn to control it. I'm sure. Until then. We'll lock the gates. We'll reduce the staff.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，我们会保护她，她能做到的，相信我。在她学会控制之前，我们会锁上城门，裁去城内人员。

yingyinNormal.en: You can't force me. Oh, yes, I can. First I'll lock you in this room and then when he's arrived, I'll tear the clothes from your body and hold you down, if that's what it takes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不能强迫我 ，我当然能。我会先把你锁在这屋里，然后等医生来，我会撕掉你的衣服，把你按在地上，如果有这必要的话。

yingyinNormal.en: Anything yet? We have a signal, but there's no frame lock.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有什么了吗？我们有信号，却不能锁定坐标。

yingyinNormal.en: Hobbs and Riley went to lock down the base. They're gonna meet us there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 霍布斯和莱丽已经去封锁基地，他们会在那见我们。

yingyinNormal.en: This is an ordinary top hat. You've chosen that card freely. I do not have a set of lock picks lodged in my keister.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是一顶普通的礼帽哦，这张牌是你随便抽的哦，我的屁眼里可没夹着开锁工具哦。

yingyinNormal.en: You park on the edge of the Neutral Zone, you lock onto Harrison's position, you fire, you kill him and you haul ass.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你把飞船停在中立区边缘，然后锁定哈里森的位置，开火，杀了他就把飞船开回来。

yingyinNormal.en: There was even a plan. We were going to throw his kindle outside, and when he went to get it, lock the door and let him freeze to death.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们甚至有过计划，我们打算把他的炉子扔到外头，等他出去捡的时候，把门锁上，冻死他。

yingyinNormal.en: Underneath, through the ring, lock it off. Tighten. And pay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 从下面穿过这个环，拉好，绑紧，然后付钱。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, yeah, okay, me, too. Zip it, lock it. Put it in your pocket.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，我也是，嘴巴拉上，闭紧，放在兜里。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, if we could lock up Virginia... It would send a very big message.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我们能拿下弗吉尼亚，就会向全国发出强势的讯息。

yingyinNormal.en: Here we go, lock up your daughter. We're going to hit them and quit them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太对了，看好女儿哦，不然我们上完可不买账哦。

yingyinNormal.en: If I'm gonna lock up this nomination for you, I deserve to be compensated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要是帮你拿下了提名，我应该得到报酬。

yingyinNormal.en: Now you listen to me. I know you feel like you can't find someone, but there's a lock for every key.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在你给我听好，我知道你感觉自己注定是剩男，但每个问题都有解决方法。

yingyinNormal.en: You need the Emperor in order to accomplish your final design. You cannot lock me away from him forever.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为了实现你的大业，你总会需要皇上的圣旨，所以你不可能一直不让我见他。

yingyinNormal.en: At any rate, she can hardly grow any worse. If she does, we'd be obliged to lock her up for the rest of her life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论怎样，她再坏也坏不到哪里去。如果她变得更加差劲，我们有义务将她一辈子关在家里。

yingyinNormal.en: Let me lock in that trade right now and get back to you with my secretary with an exact confirmation. Sound good, John?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我这就去把这笔交易定下来再让我秘书和你进一步确认，可以吧，John？

examination_example.sentence: Museums <highlight>locked</highlight> some of them away in the dark.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 博物馆将其中一些锁在暗处。

examination_example.sentence: The strategy also aims to ensure that carbon in woody material is <highlight>locked</highlight> away in the form of solid lumber or burned as biofuel in vehicles.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该战略还旨在确保木质材料中的碳以固体木材的形式被封存，或作为生物燃料在车辆中燃烧。

examination_example.sentence: And while you may forgive your smart phone an occasional fault, you probably have less patience for error messages from your door <highlight>lock</highlight>.
